{{Isuzu Ren|Infobox}}

{{Description
| en = A magical girl who has trouble talking to people and has been shy since she was little.<br/>Due to her isolation and the suffering she felt living every day, she was at the end of her rope, but after discovering the world of magical girls, she was able to pull herself up from rock bottom.<br/>She has grown emotionally, but there are still times when she is timid.
| jp = 小さい頃から内気で、人と話すことが苦手な魔法少女。<br/>孤立し、生きていくことに苦しみ、自らを追い詰めてしまうが、<br/>その時に魔法少女の世界を知ったことで、<br/>どん底から抜け出すことができた。<br/>精神的に成長もするが、まだ気弱な所がある。
}}

{{Tabs}}
[[Category:Puella Magi]]
[[Category:Characters]]
[[Category:Has a Doppel]]
[[Category:Unlimited]]

{{Misono Karin|Infobox}}

{{Description
| en = A self-styled magical girl born on Halloween.<br/>Her characteristic is dreamy and tends to interpret things as she likes, and combining the hobby of reading and drawing manga, she has created her design as a magical girl.<br/>She was influenced by her favorite manga ''Phantom Thief Girl Magical Kirin''.
| jp = 自称、ハロウィンが生んだ魔法少女。<br/>夢見がちで都合良く解釈しようとする性格と、漫画の読み描きという趣味が相まって、魔法少女としての設定を作ってしまった。<br/>“怪盗少女マジカルきりん”というお気に入りの漫画に影響されている。
}}

