{{Sakura Kyouko|Infobox}}

{{Description
| en = A magical girl from Kazamino City.<br/>She does not seem to attend school, and nobody knows where she lives.<br/>Due to her self-centered personality and pragmatism, she often clashes with other girls.<br/>She's usually seen eating something.<br/>Her weapon is an articulated spear. She is also able to cast barrier magic.
| jp = 風見野市出身の魔法少女。<br/>学校に通っている様子はなく、どこに住んでいるかも分からない。<br/>勝気な性格とドライな価値観から、他の少女たちと衝突することが多い。<br/>普段はいつも何かを食べている。<br/>武器は多関節の槍。結界魔法も使える。
}}

