{{Tatsuki Asuka|Infobox}}
{{Description
| en = A magical girl that is an assistant naginata instructor and trains daily to become a master of the art. She is the only daughter of a family that runs a dojo with a long history called "Ryuushinkan."<br/>While she follows the rules and makes it a principle to be honest, she also has a thoughtless, careless side that can sometimes cause an uproar.
| jp = 薙刀術の師範代で、免許皆伝を目指して日々稽古を重ねている魔法<br/>少女。長い歴史を持つ武術道場「竜真館」の一人娘。<br/>規律を守り、常に清廉を旨としているが、迂闊でそそっかしい一面も<br/>持ち、そのことで騒動を引き起こしてしまうことがある。
}}
